{
  "stem": "747.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the Nazis started to come to power, this guy-- his name was Gyula-- he became a big shot.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "All of the sudden he became a somebody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we were scared of him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Scared-- he went overboard with the hatred.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1930-- after '39, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the Nazi-- the Nazi-- Hungarian Nazi party officially came into being.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they signed up, all these young kids.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not all, but many of them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they had a miserable home, or they had no home life-- something was missing from their lives, so they find that was a kick for them-- it was a big excitement, wearing uniform.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they got the gun.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were dangerous.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were big signs all over town-- 'Jews, go to Palestine.' We would love to go, if we could.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But unfortunately, we couldn't, because there was a restriction there, too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "With the White Paper-- and we just couldn't get out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, we did dear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Of course we heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a biased-- before the war-- it was all biased.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Kristallnacht, of course we knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And was-- in Austria, an event was the Anschluss, when the-- which Nazis marched into Austria.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the-- the-- he committed suicide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was his name?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What-- can't remember-- it's starting with a D.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't recall his name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all of the sudden, it's-- it just became hell on earth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Austrians just went on a rampage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the--the Jews-- had no mercy for the Jews.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The stores were closed, and they took everyday livelihood.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was before our turn.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we heard about their plight.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
